 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Direct upgrade to True Thrust after successfully landing the last combo action, i.e. Drakesbane. The True Thrust button will temporarily be replaced by this 320 potency action. Grants a stack of Firstminds&amp;rsquo; Focus at Level 90.&lt;/td>
