 &lt;td style="text-align: left">96&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">250 potency action that combos off of True Thrust/Raiden Thrust and applies a 10% damage buff for 30s. Direct upgrade to Disembowel, replacing the original action.&lt;/td>
