 &lt;td style="text-align: left">The fifth and final combo action after Fang and Claw and Wheeling Thrust with 440 potency. Grants Draconian Fire for 30s, turning True Thrust into Raiden Thrust and Doom Spike into Draconian Fury.&lt;/td>
